sub_title: Member of the Executive Board - International Sales & BD at Kekelit GmbH Austria
summary:
A number of international, commercial management roles in companies (groups) supplying innovative products in the building market, in which new business areas and/or regional areas had to be developed, as well as current customer- and product bases have to be maintained.

Specialties: Business to business commercial management; working with agents and wholesaler structures. International experience, on a worldwide basis.
